<quantity box="[662,746,511,537]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.05" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="0.1" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" unit="m" value="20.5" valueMax="40.0" valueMin="1.0">1–40 m</quantity>
depth on sandy or gravel bottoms nearby rock beds or seagrass (
<bibRefCitation author="Louisy, P." box="[159,304,546,573]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" refId="ref60639" refString="Louisy, P. (2015) Europe and Mediterranean Marine Fish Identification Guide. 3 rd Edition. Eugen Ulmer Ed., Paris, 512 pp." type="book" year="2015">Louisy 2015</bibRefCitation>
